---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A line of only pipes is plain text, never a table:

|

||

|||

A table stops at a following pipe-only line:

<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><p>a</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

|

A pipe-only line before a table stays a paragraph:

|

<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><p>b</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
